	- @done Implement PingService — TCP-based latency via NWConnection to configurable target (default 1.1.1.1:443) @done(2026-06-22)
	- @done Gate PingService behind LicenseManager.isPaid @done(2026-06-22)
	- @done Implement ping/latency display in popover (ms readout, toggle on/off) @done(2026-06-22)
	- @done Add Settings tab: IP refresh mode and interval, ping target configuration @done(2026-06-22)
