	- @done Write unit tests for IPService (mock DNS responses, caching behavior, refresh modes, failure handling) @done(2026-06-22)
	- @done Write unit tests for PingService (mock NWConnection, latency reporting, start/stop lifecycle) @done(2026-06-22)
	- @done Add VoiceOver accessibility labels to all Phase 3 UI elements @done(2026-06-22)
	- @done All user-facing strings use String(localized:) @done(2026-06-22)
	- @done Update .taskpaper with any discoveries or adjustments @done(2026-06-22)
	- Manual test against PRD user stories 29-32 (IP features)
	- Manual test against PRD user stories 33-35 (Ping features)
	- Manual test against PRD user story 31 (copy IP to clipboard)
	- Regression test: all Phase 1-2 user stories
	Discoveries:
		- Raw DNS over UDP via NWConnection works well for external IP — no need for libresolv or shelling out
		- Swift 6 strict concurrency: NWConnection callbacks need thread-safe continuation handling (ContinuationGate pattern with NSLock)
		- LicenseManager changed from final to open class with internal(set) isPaid for test subclassing
		- Local IP resolution moved from NetworkMonitor to IPService to establish proper module ownership per PRD
		- DetailRow copyable pattern: adding copyable:true flag to existing view component avoids copy-paste code across IP displays

